stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Loading
  Loading --> Ready: content loaded
  Loading --> Error: load failure

  Ready --> Viewing
  Viewing --> Viewing: swipe next/prev
  Viewing --> Sharing: share tapped
  Sharing --> Viewing: share completed/cancelled
  Viewing --> GeneratingAudio: TTS play
  GeneratingAudio --> Viewing: stop/complete
  Viewing --> [*]: app closed
  Error --> Ready: retry succeeds
